***********************************
* Setup a reflection for packages *
***********************************


All commands to type into terminal are written after $ sign.
Open up terminal and run following commands:

# Update your system's database
$ sudo pacman -Syy

# Set mirrors for your country
$ reflector -c 'Your-Country' -f 12 -l 12 -n 12 --verbose --save /etc/pacman.d/mirrorlist
